  <h3 class="group-title" id="contact-information">Contact information</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>If you need help with the Kickstart Scheme process, you can contact:</p>

<ul>
  <li>your local employer contact if you are located in a specific region</li>
  <li>the national employer contact if you are located across several regions</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>


